      "comment": "SHREWD ETHICS (1) was among the minors three back at Maitland then missed the frame the last two, but drawn box 1 this time where she has two wins. Can turn form around here. BUGATTI RICO (2) showed good pace from out wide and was prominent throughout before fading out of it when 6th at this track in a Grade 5. Form here at this distance is sound. Likely to be about the money. CALLA MUFFIN (8) finds it hard to win. Finished in the money last time though when third (18.77) at Richmond. Solid record here at this trip including four wins. Expected to be in the finish again. SCOTT WEDNESDAY (3) will give backers a sight.",
